load ../harness-class.maude

--- Coverage: a context-assembly knob configures a Managed agent.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-CLASS :
  managed compactionKnob
  =>* managed configured .

--- Coverage: a delegation knob configures a Delegated agent.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-CLASS :
  delegated settingsKnob
  =>* delegated configured .

--- Bite: a delegation knob never configures a Managed agent. The RESIDUAL soup var
--- makes a `configured` in ANY reachable state a solution, so No solution proves the
--- wrong-class knob never takes effect (it is rejected, not silently applied).
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-CLASS :
  managed settingsKnob
  =>* configured RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: a context-assembly knob never configures a Delegated agent.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-CLASS :
  delegated compactionKnob
  =>* configured RESIDUAL:Cfg .
